  "summary": {
    "en": "An exploration of the halachic requirement to face Jerusalem during prayer, examining the biblical foundations from King Solomon's Temple dedication to Daniel's practice in exile, with practical guidance on determining direction anywhere in the world using modern technology and traditional methods.",
